---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Kay's Kustom Metal Works">
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"> -->
      <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Kay's Kustom Metal Works</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            For over a decade, Kay's Kustom Metal Works has been the trusted source for high-quality parts for classic cars. Our passion for automotive excellence drives us to create parts that not only meet but exceed the standards of classic car enthusiasts.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Our founder, Lee Kay, started this business with a simple mission: to provide classic car owners with the highest quality parts that maintain the authenticity and integrity of their vehicles. With years of experience in metalworking and a deep understanding of classic car mechanics, Kay ensures that every part that leaves our shop meets the highest standards of quality and craftsmanship.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            At Kay's Kustom Metal Works, we understand that classic cars are more than just vehicles - they're pieces of history. That's why we take great pride in our work, ensuring that every part we create helps preserve the legacy of these automotive treasures.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3">
            <img
              src="/imgs/owner.jpg"
              alt="Kay - Owner of Kay's Kustom Metal Works"
              class="object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>
        </div> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our Commitment to Quality</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔧</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Expert Craftsmanship</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Every part is crafted with precision and attention to detail, ensuring perfect fit and finish.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">⚙️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Premium Materials</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We use only the highest quality materials to ensure durability and authenticity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚗</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Classic Car Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our deep understanding of classic cars ensures parts that maintain original specifications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 